r5692 | sonicz | 2011-09-20 05:09:59 -0400 (Tue, 20 Sep 2011) | 8 lines

Fix bug[#6797] ldr-utils: Split bss section into ldr zero-fill blocks according to predefined size.

BF53x and BF561 bootrom doesn't support load and fill ldr blocks that is larger than
64k bytes. The max block size is defined in ldr utility. If bss section is larger than
this size, split it into several zero-fill blocks.



